<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="550" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="0.[1240,2119,810,1040]" pageId="0" pageNumber="550">• Medium-sized to large monkeys with long trunk,ischial callosities, narrow nasal opening and palate, daggerlike canines, molars with two ridges, and tail lacking or short in some, long in most; males usually larger than females.</paragraph>
<caption box="[1240,1447,1007,1040]" inLine="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="550" startId="0.[1240,1253,1007,1040]" targetBox="[1492,1720,976,1169]" targetPageId="0">
